      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼采葛兮，一日不見，如三月兮。
彼采蕭兮，一日不見，如三秋兮。
彼采艾兮，一日不見，如三歲兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>1 There he is gathering the dolichos !
A day without seeing him
Is like three months !

2 There he is gathering the oxtail-southernwood !
A day without seeing him
Is like three seasons !

3 There he is gathering the mugwort !
A day without seeing him
Is like three years !</seg>
      </tuv>
